    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 101.</p><p>Tier II: Great Keeper</p><p>Prerequisite: Soul of the World</p><p>Primordial Intellect. You gain proficiency on Intelligence, Wisdom, and Charisma saving throws.</p><p>Regain Sense. As a bonus action on your turn, you can end a single condition affecting you or an ally within 30 feet among the following: charmed, frightened, stunned, or any condition originating from a spell of the Enchantment school.</p><p>Wisdom of the Keeper. You learn one 8th-level spell and one 9th-level spell from any class list. Wisdom is your spellcasting ability for these spells.</p></div>",
